    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. i've also heard some people say that originalism is basically just a way for judges to push a specific political agenda under the guise of law. do you think those criticisms are valid, or is that just a misunderstanding of the theory?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
